body: "Implemented pm brief next --explain with deterministic score/dependency breakdown output, updated docs, and added tests for explain mode and ranking details. Validation passed via npm test and npm run typecheck.\n\nAdded brief insights UX layer: missing focus IDs, closed-focus omission notices, and filter mismatch guidance with remediation commands. Updated index.ts, README.md, and tests; validated with npm run typecheck and npm test."
